snippet.title: Johnny Depp Predicts His Relationship With Amber Heard in 10 Seconds
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp met Amber Heard on the set of The Rum Diary and correctly predicted how things would end and how we all feel about their relationship today in 10 seconds. 

This is probably one of the best Johnny Depp quotes on love from one of the best Johnny Depp movies and it's just bizarre that he perfectly sums up the end of their relationship before it even began. 

Being a movie nerd I love things like this and because this is one of the best Johnny Depp moments about the Amber Heard Rum Diary character, based on the novel from one of his best friends, Hunter S. Thompson captures how things would end between these two so well that I think it is a fantastic Johnny Depp or Amber Heard meme.
